But should having a job make up for all the chaos, destruction and death Trump has inflicted on our nation?
As a small business owner, the GOP tax bill Trump signed into law, which has benefited me economically, is probably the equivalent to a job for others.
Trump threatens all of that, putting at risk the republic in which my Latina girlfriend and I are raising two multi-ethnic daughters.
There are so many forces pushing us to think the way Trump does, the way Baldonado encourages.
The Republican Party I once respected is dead.